---
import { t, changeLanguage } from "i18next";
import { Trans } from "astro-i18next/components";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ContactCTA from "../components/ContactCTA.astro";
import CvCTA from "../components/CvCTA.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import Icon from "../components/Icon.astro";

changeLanguage("en");
---

<BaseLayout title={t("site.abouts")} description={t("site.aboutd")}>
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title={t("about.title")}
				tagline={t("about.titled")}
			>
				<img
					width="512"
					height="512"
					src="/assets/at-work.webp"
					alt="Davide Di Marsilio"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						<Trans i18nKey="about.text1">
						I am an <strong>System Administrator</strong> with almost 3 years of experience in various IT fields. I possess knowledge in handling <strong>Azure, Active Directory, Operating Systems, and troubleshooting</strong> a wide range of software-related problems. Additionally, I have worked as a <strong>Control Room operator</strong>, leveraging my skills in monitoring softwares like Nagios.
						</Trans>
					</p>
					<p>
						<Trans i18nKey="about.text2">
						<strong>Computer science</strong> have been an integral part of my life since childhood and a life long passion, as I began using PCs with Windows 98. I am deeply passionate about this field and constantly strive to <strong>expand my knowledge through continuous learning</strong>. One of my ambitions is to work as a <strong>system administrator</strong>, where I can utilize my expertise to tackle complex IT challenges and ensure optimal system performance.
						</Trans>
					</p>
					<p>
						<br>
						<Trans i18nKey="about.text3">
						In addition to my IT skills, I am a <strong>self-taught artist</strong> proficient in <strong>graphic logo design and various artistic endeavors</strong>. Since the beginning of my journey in the artistic world, I have honed my skills in <strong>Photoshop and Illustrator</strong>. I thoroughly enjoy creating designs for companies, websites, t-shirts, and numerous other platforms and applications. Creating art allows me to express <strong>myself creatively and combine it with my technical skills</strong> to make beautiful and significant designs for clients.
						</Trans>
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">{t("about.exp")}</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<h2>System Administrator & End-user service - <a href="https://www.brembo.com/" target="_blank">Brembo</a> c/o <a href="https://www.ecit.it/" target="_blank">ECIT S.p.A.</a></h2>
					<h2 style="color:var(--gray-300);">Inizio 2024 | Full-time</h2>
					<p><Icon icon="list-check" size="1.33em" /> Ticket management via the Service Now platform</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="user-folder" size="1.33em" /> Active Directory and Domain Administrator: creating administrative and onboarding users, groups, OUs, network folder permissions management, Device Lock management, Group Policies and DHCP Server</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="square-four" size="1.33em" /> Full management of all MS services: Azure, Intune, Teams Administrator, Exchange Online Administrator, Microsoft 365 Security, Microsoft Admin Portal</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="code" size="1.33em" /> Automation and scripting with Powershell and Python</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="phone-call" size="1.33em" /> Creation and management of critical tickets to Microsoft support in English</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="network" size="1.33em" /> Basic knowledge of Networks and Networking</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="hard-drives" size="1.33em" /> Basic knowledge of SCCM</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="cloud" size="1.33em" /> Using Citrix for session management and app virtualization</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="headset" size="1.33em" /> Admin side management for various enterprise applications and remote support applications (Bomgar)</p>
					<br>
					<h2>HelpDesk - <a href="https://www.europassistance.it/" target="_blank">Europassistance</a> c/o <a href="https://www.ecit.it/" target="_blank">ECIT S.p.A.</a></h2>
					<h2 style="color:var(--gray-300);">Early 2023 | Full-time</h2>
					<p><Icon icon="list-check" size="1.33em" /> Ticket management via the Mantis platform</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="user-folder" size="1.33em" /> Active Directory, Windows Server 2016 - 2019</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="windows" size="1.33em" /> Creating, managing and configuring Distribution Lists and Shared Mailboxes via Exchange Online and OnPremise</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="teams" size="1.33em" /> Knowledge of Sharepoint platforms, MS Teams</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="square-four" size="1.33em" /> Knowledge of Azure and MS Intune</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="identification-badge" size="1.33em" /> Partial management of corporate Identity Governance</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="desktop-tower" size="1.33em" />Headquarters support in preparing, installing and organizing meeting rooms for video conferencing</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="phone-call" size="1.33em" /> Handling incoming and outgoing technical support calls and emails</p>
					<br>
					<h2>HelpDesk - <a href="https://www.centrostyle.com/" target="_blank">Centrostyle</a> c/o <a href="https://www.ecit.it/" target="_blank">ECIT S.p.A.</a></h2>
					<h2 style="color:var(--gray-300);">Inizio 2023</h2>
					<p><Icon icon="list-check" size="1.33em" /> Ticket management via the Jira platform</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="desktop-tower" size="1.33em" /> Assistance on on-site hardware installation</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="printer" size="1.33em" /> Assistance on printer installation and enterprise software for end users</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="computer-tower" size="1.33em" /> Installation of end-user workstations</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="square-four" size="1.33em" /> Enterprise hardware preparation: OS installation, BIOS upgrade and more</p>
					<br>
					<h2>Control Room Operator - <a href="https://www.luxottica.com/" target="_blank">Luxottica</a> c/o <a href="https://www.ecit.it/" target="_blank">ECIT S.p.A.</a></h2>
					<h2 style="color:var(--gray-300);">Early 2021 | Full-time</h2>
					<p><Icon icon="pulse" size="1.33em" /> Management via Nagios and Solarwind monitoring platform</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="code" size="1.33em" /> Creating scripts for Nagios and automation scripts with Python and Bash</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="linux-logo" size="1.33em" /> Installing agents on Windows and Linux machines</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="hard-drives" size="1.33em" /> Monitoring network equipment such as Switches, Routers, Firewalls and Virtual Machines</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="phone-call" size="1.33em" /> Handling international English-language calls for critical issues</p>
                    <p><Icon icon="square-four" size="1.33em" /> Extensive use of Office suite: Excel, Word, Outlook</p>
					<br>
					<h2>Recording Studio Technician - <a href="https://ilclandestinogiornale.italiasera.it/" target="_blank">DComunication</a></h2>
					<h2 style="color:var(--gray-300);">Late 2019 | Fixed-term full-time</h2>
					<p><Icon icon="video" size="1.33em" /> Video & Photo Editing</p>
					<p><Icon icon="film-reel" size="1.33em" /> Directing for local television shows and broadcasts</p>
					<p><Icon icon="video-camera" size="1.33em" /> Cameraman</p>
					<p><Icon icon="code" size="1.33em" /> Internal website development (wordpress) and grapich design</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">{t("about.cert")}</h2>
					<div>
					<h2>Azure Fundamentals - AZ-900</h2>
					<p><strong><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/certifications/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">Microsoft</a></strong></p>
					<p><strong>Summer 2022 - <Icon icon="certificate" size="1.33em" /><a href="https://www.credly.com/badges/1e4a40d9-096f-4382-b468-5fb8188e41b3/linked_in_profile" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"> Certification</a></strong></p>
					<br>
					<h2>Active Directory & Windows Server 2019</h2>
					<p><strong><a href="https://www.udemy.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">Udemy</a></strong></p>
					<p><strong>Mid 2019 - <Icon icon="certificate" size="1.33em" /><a href="https://www.udemy.com/certificate/UC-b5498972-c63b-4226-aadb-3ebd5c990977/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"> Certification</a></strong></p>
					<br>
					<h2>CSS, JavaScript And Python Complete Course</h2>
					<p><strong><a href="https://www.udemy.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">Udemy</a></strong></p>
					<p><strong>Mid 2019 - <Icon icon="certificate" size="1.33em" /><a href="https://www.udemy.com/certificate/UC-129e3880-ddaa-4421-ba45-62b91546769e/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"> Certification</a></strong></p>
					<br>
					<h2>EIPASS IT Security</h2>
					<p><strong><a href="https://en.eipass.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">EIPASS</a></strong></p>
					<p><strong>Late 2020 - <Icon icon="certificate" size="1.33em" /><a href="/documents/EIPASS IT Security - Davide Di Marsilio.pdf" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"> Certification</a></strong></p>
					<br>
					<h2>EIPASS 7 Moduli User</h2>
					<p><strong><a href="https://en.eipass.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">EIPASS</a></strong></p>
					<p><strong>Late 2020 - <Icon icon="certificate" size="1.33em" /><a href="/documents/EIPASS 7 Moduli User - Davide Di Marsilio.pdf" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"> Certification</a></strong></p>
					<br>
					<h2>Adobe Premiere Pro</h2>
					<p><strong><a href="https://www.udemy.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">Udemy</a></strong></p>
					<p><strong>Mid 2019 - <Icon icon="certificate" size="1.33em" /><a href="https://www.udemy.com/certificate/UC-PVZPEVI1/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"> Certification</a></strong></p>
					<br>
					<h2>B2 First - Score 162</h2>
					<p><strong><a href="https://www.cambridge.org/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">Cambridge University</a></strong></p>
					<p><strong>Mid 2017 - <Icon icon="certificate" size="1.33em" /><a href="/documents/B2 First - Davide Di Marsilio.pdf" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"> Certification</a></strong></p>
					</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				
				<h2 class="section-title">{t("about.edu")}</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<h2 style="color: var(--gray-300);">ITIS Luigi Trafelli</h2>
					<h2 style="color: var(--gray-300);">2013 - 2018</h2>
				</div>
				
			</section>
		</main>
		<CvCTA />
		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>

	h2{
		font-size: var(--text-l);
	}
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		max-width: 60%;
    	height: auto;
    	margin-left: auto;
    	margin-right: auto;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
